# Offer Builder System

This rule provides context for working with the offer builder system in benefits-svc.

## Overview

The Offer Builder is a **data-driven UI system** for creating offers/rewards. It operates independently of Journey Builder but can be embedded within journeys.

For detailed guides, see `offer-builder/*.md` in this workspace.

## Key Tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `synthetic_reward_types` | What reward types exist (comped item, discount, ride credit) |
| `offer_builder_flows` | Which steps for a reward_type × platform × audience_type |
| `offer_builder_flow_steps` | Links flows to steps with ordering |
| `offer_builder_steps` | Reusable step definitions (step_type, default_title) |
| `offer_builder_flow_step_elements` | Links flow_steps to elements |
| `offer_builder_elements` | Input field definitions |
| `offer_builder_element_options` | Dropdown/switch options |

