## Common Step Types

| step_type | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `reward_selection` | Select comped item from menu |
| `reward_creation` | Configure discount/credit amount |
| `audience_definition` | Select audience (standalone flows) |
| `program_settings` | Redemption limits, duration |
| `messaging` | Checkout message (discounts) |
| `item_messaging` | SMS for comped item delivery |
| `messaging_sms` | SMS message step |
| `confirmation` | Review before creating |
| `success_handoff` | Success screen |

